Balance-mode can be used to keep track of checking accounts.  It is a modified version of the balance-mode.el by Bob Newell and Jason Baietto.  It is available at
http://vh213601.truman.edu/~belanger/Elisp/balance.el
A simplified version, http://vh213601.truman.edu/~belanger/Elisp/credit-card.el
can keep track of credit cards.

----
CategoryFinancial 
